ord !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　你可能要说，都是唐朝的美人，妆容造型哪会有什么区别？</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　从 人物塑造上来讲，娇若无骨的杨玉环和气盖河山的武则天怎么可能会是一个样子？但是从历史背景来说，杨贵妃算起来应该是武则天的孙媳妇（历史不及格的小伙伴 们请自行百度），两人年龄不过相差几十年而已，当时所流行的妆容、发型确实应该是相差无几的，所以也怪不了范冰冰饰演的两人，造型如此相像，傻傻分不清 呢！</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　那么，杨贵妃和武媚娘的妆容发型到底应该是什么样子的呢？</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/dUr78dERRBOzBsx8RmsGTDFib6DGy8EicciaBkYewdibl3gKKs1bUmWgk7tQibNNGC4X5cuYicG0mjkvvXwntr49K0hA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.0112359550561798\" data-w=\"445\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 80, 77); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 