lay: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2015年8月22日</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 129, 189); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">痛惜！5岁女孩过马路被公交车撞死 母亲当场哭晕…</span></strong></p></section></section><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section data-width=\"0px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><p><br></p>\n<p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\">8月22日晚，四川攀枝花一5岁女孩和母亲回家时，独自跑到公路上，被一辆公交车撞倒碾压身亡，母亲痛哭晕厥。有目击者称，当时母亲在看手机，没注意孩子，孩子独自跑到了马路上…再次提醒家长，出门请放下手机，看好孩子！（来自：人民日报——华西都市报）</p>\n<p style=\"\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vRaVWGC0F61icMicO11to0xj8Sgfdoexia40DvbrjVea1OgTdLyjTcvyJyEBqxMf1aCuianicjQZFZHOZl4jIObic0fA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.585\" data-w=\"400\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85738\" data-color=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" data-custom=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" style=\"\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 670px; border: none; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"70%\" style=\"margin: -5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; width: 457.79827880859375px; float: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2015年8月21日</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 129, 189); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">妈妈看手机的工夫 儿子被轧身亡</span></strong></p></section></section><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section data-width=\"0px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><p><br></p>\n<p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\">8月21日下午，郑州某商场楼下，一2岁男童玩耍时被一驶离停车场的轿车碾压，抢救无效死亡。肇事司机已被带走调查。目击者称，孩子妈妈出事前正看手机，不在身边，一会儿工夫，孩子跑到了车辆右前轮位置…（来自：人民日报）</p>\n<p style=\"\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vRaVWGC0F61icMicO11to0xj8Sgfdoexia4TiaHknkESawvJBoQmgAeyFwd3w0SNLoQqqHhrWzhPCOuZmiaACMfaoWg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"440\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85738\" data-color=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" data-custom=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" style=\"\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 670px; border: none; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"70%\" style=\"margin: -5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; width: 457.79827880859375px; float: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2015年8月21日</span></section><sectio